Class TripleWithDirection

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class TripleWithDirection
extends org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple5<GradoopId,GradoopId,GradoopId,Boolean,boolean[]>
    Represents an edge-source-target triple and its query candidates. f0: edge id f1: source vertex id f2: target vertex id f3: outgoing edge flag (true if outgoing, false if incoming) f4: query candidates
